---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import { Clock, Zap, Dumbbell, Flame, Target } from 'lucide-astro';

const day1 = [
  { exercise: "Press de Banca con Mancuernas", sets: "4", reps: "8-10" },
  { exercise: "Press Militar Sentado", sets: "3", reps: "10-12" },
  { exercise: "Aperturas con Mancuernas", sets: "3", reps: "12-15" },
  { exercise: "Extensiones de Tríceps", sets: "3", reps: "12-15" }
];

const day2 = [
  { exercise: "Remo con Mancuerna a una mano", sets: "4", reps: "8-10" },
  { exercise: "Pájaros (Hombro Posterior)", sets: "3", reps: "15" },
  { exercise: "Curl de Bíceps Alterno", sets: "3", reps: "10-12" },
  { exercise: "Martillo", sets: "2", reps: "12-15" }
];

const day3 = [
  { exercise: "Sentadilla Goblet", sets: "4", reps: "10-12" },
  { exercise: "Peso Muerto Rumano (Mancuernas)", sets: "4", reps: "8-10" },
  { exercise: "Zancadas Estáticas", sets: "3", reps: "12 por pierna" },
  { exercise: "Elevación de Gemelos", sets: "4", reps: "15-20" }
];
---

<Layout title="Rutina Push/Pull/Legs en Casa | MicroGym Elite" description="La rutina de división más efectiva adaptada para entrenar en casa con mancuernas. Maximiza la hipertrofia dividiendo tus grupos musculares.">
  <Navbar />
  
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-primary font-black tracking-widest text-[10px] uppercase">RUTINA AVANZADA</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl mt-4 mb-8 leading-tight">Push / Pull / Legs: <span class="text-gradient">Hipertrofia</span> en Casa</h1>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Clock class="text-primary" size={20} />
            <div>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-text-dim block uppercase font-bold">Sesión</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold">60 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Target class="text-primary" size={20} />
            <div>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-text-dim block uppercase font-bold">Objetivo</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold">Músculo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Dumbbell class="text-primary" size={20} />
            <div>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-text-dim block uppercase font-bold">Equipo</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold">Mancuernas + Banco</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Flame class="text-primary" size={20} />
            <div>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-text-dim block uppercase font-bold">Días</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold">3-6 días/sem</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-12 text-text-muted">
        <p class="text-lg">
          La división Push/Pull/Legs (Empuje/Tracción/Pierna) es posiblemente la forma más lógica y efectiva de organizar el entrenamiento de fuerza. Al agrupar los músculos que trabajan juntos, permites un descanso óptimo y una frecuencia de entrenamiento adaptable.
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-text font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Zap class="text-primary" /> Día 1: Empuje (Pecho, Hombro, Tríceps)
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5">
            <table class="w-full text-left">
              <thead class="bg-white/5 text-text uppercase text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest">
                <tr><th class="p-4">Ejercicio</th><th class="p-4">Series</th><th class="p-4">Reps</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-sm">
                {day1.map(ex => (
                  <tr><td class="p-4 text-text font-bold">{ex.exercise}</td><td class="p-4">{ex.sets}</td><td class="p-4">{ex.reps}</td></tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-text font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Zap class="text-primary" /> Día 2: Tracción (Espalda, Bíceps)
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5">
            <table class="w-full text-left">
              <thead class="bg-white/5 text-text uppercase text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest">
                <tr><th class="p-4">Ejercicio</th><th class="p-4">Series</th><th class="p-4">Reps</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-sm">
                {day2.map(ex => (
                  <tr><td class="p-4 text-text font-bold">{ex.exercise}</td><td class="p-4">{ex.sets}</td><td class="p-4">{ex.reps}</td></tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl text-text font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <Zap class="text-primary" /> Día 3: Piernas
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5">
            <table class="w-full text-left">
              <thead class="bg-white/5 text-text uppercase text-[10px] font-black tracking-widest">
                <tr><th class="p-4">Ejercicio</th><th class="p-4">Series</th><th class="p-4">Reps</th></tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-sm">
                {day3.map(ex => (
                  <tr><td class="p-4 text-text font-bold">{ex.exercise}</td><td class="p-4">{ex.sets}</td><td class="p-4">{ex.reps}</td></tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>



